Hi,
    I tested 2.5.67-ac2 with two continuous drive reset call,
dmesged out oops messages as below. system didn't crash
like under 2.4.21-pre1-ac1, but that race still exist.
    oops message:
hda: DMA disabled
------------[ cut here ]------------
